{"tid":1356411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過最需要遍地開花既地方，其實係連登","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:26:32.000Z","uid":114801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2410468d8f4e278bbc76325826e3fe4fff03c41","tid":1356411,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"戰線、資訊實在太多<br />\n自己友同自己友鬥推時事台，長久下去，唔係辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟有個小小愚見，不如響連登遍地開花啦<br />\n<br />\n一方面可以將反送中運動宣揚去無上時事台既人身上（一定有呢種，仲要成堆）<br />\n另一方面可以減輕時事台負擔，留番比主線<br />\n<br />\n上班台；罷工<br />\n飲食台：日牛，吉野家etc<br />\n創意台：改歌、惡搞<br />\n影視台：追擊TVB (忍撚左入面班TVB打手好耐）<br />\n體育台：練武<br />\n潮流台：迪卡農裝備討論<br />\n<br />\n唔建議太散，可嘗試先集中抽呢幾個台出黎做分流。其他諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點？"},{"pid":"1c5a00effe87f62cabf57c3b519212573e4a5115","tid":1356411,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"睇唔切咁多個台"},{"pid":"008a9b407f7e7fbef17f641a62ae87e4a7cf6466","tid":1356411,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2ju6hY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2ju6hY.png&h=f48ee3d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oz19mRi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOz19mRi.png&h=d417b731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好掛住花生<br />\n都要推重要野!!"},{"pid":"cac5dbc3b76f6ca574d043a65afc70cbbe1ce1d0","tid":1356411,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5a00effe87f62cabf57c3b519212573e4a5115","tid":1356411,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"睇唔切咁多個台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"有需要先去睇<br />\n<br />\n例如迪卡農裝備，大把人已經齊裝"}]}